msgid "Intro Weex Syntax"
msgstr "介绍weex语法 "

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/tutorial.md:64
msgid ""
"So it's time for some \"boring syntax\", as content of tech_list.we showing, "
"Weex source code is written in three parts -- *template*, *style*, *script* "
"just like html,css,javascript for the Web."
msgstr ""
"是时候聊聊无趣的语法了，tech_list.we 代码分三部分 - 模板(template), 样式"
"(style), 脚本(script)；正如 HTML，CSS，JavaScript 之于 Web 。 "

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/tutorial.md:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "Template is the skeleton that give weex structure, it composed by tags which surround content and apply meaning to it. Weex has two type of tag, opening tag & closing tag, we call every couple  of opening tag &  closing tag a Weex tag. Tag have *attributes*,  different attribute have different meaning,   class attribute makes it possible to define equal styles for multiple tags,  onclick attribute makes the tag  responds to click  event.\n"
msgstr "模板是weex结构的骨架，它由各式各样的标签组成。weex的标签有两部分，标签开始和标签结束，我们称每对开始和结束为一个weex标签。标签有属性，不同的属性有不同的意义，class属性可以定义一批标签的样式，onclick属性使得标签可以响应单击事件。 \n"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/tutorial.md:68
msgid ""
"Style describes how Weex tags are to be displayed. We like you, love the "
"CSS, so we try to keep consistent with CSS standard as possible. Weex Style "
"support a lot of CSS features, eg: margin, padding, fixed...... Better yet, "
"flexbox layout (flex) is well supported in Weex Style."
msgstr ""
"样式决定了weex的标签将如何显示。人人都喜欢CSS，所以我们尽量与CSS保持一致。"
"weex 的样式支持很多CSS中的特性，如：margin、padding、fixed ……  以及 flexbox "
"布局。 "

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/tutorial.md:70
msgid ""
"Script add *data* & *logic* to Weex tags, help you easy access local or "
"remote data and update tags. You can also define some methods for your tag "
"to respond to different events. Weex Script organizing learn a lot from "
"CommonJS module style."
msgstr ""
"脚本为标签定义*数据*和*逻辑*，您可以轻松访问本地或远程数据来更新标签。您还可"
"以为您的标签定义一些方法，以应响应不同的事件。weex 脚本的组织结构借鉴了很多"
"CommonJS的模块风格。 "

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/tutorial.md:72
msgid ""
"More complete information about Weex syntax can be found in our [Syntax "
"chapter](syntax/main.md)."
msgstr "关于weex语法的更多信息，请参阅[语法](syntax/main.md)。 "

